{"tid":220710,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[踢過獌聯都係禽獸] C朗強姦少女 新證據曝光","createTime":"2017-04-28T07:20:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-28T07:54:10.000Z","uid":54373,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"78caaca3d932a59752e15e23218dde32fb5d9ec7","tid":220710,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T07:20:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://m.on.cc/nc/sports/20170428/img/20170428110030sp_p3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.on.cc%2Fnc%2Fsports%2F20170428%2Fimg%2F20170428110030sp_p3.jpg&h=79835752&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【<a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=U3in%2BbByR8w%2FZmejrHnAdRv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=78e580eb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">on.cc</a>東網專訊】德國《明鏡周刊》半個月前踢爆C朗拿度2009年曾喺拉斯維加斯強姦一名少女，事後再畀37.5萬美元(約300萬港元)掩口費擺平事件，雖然C朗已經立即發聲明否認，仲話會對失實報道採取法律行動，不過《明鏡周刊》就死咬唔放，日前再度發布新證據，睇下C朗今次又會點拆？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">繼上次爆料公開一份疑似係C朗同受害人和解合約後，最新一期《明鏡周刊》再公開C朗委託律師奧蘇里奧處理呢次事件嘅協議文件，合約入面寫明奧蘇里奧將會代理C朗喺2010年1月12日處理此事(同女事主和解)，又寫明C朗拿度將會化名「Topher」，合約底部更加有C朗嘅親筆簽名！</span>"},{"pid":"33ac2ae5d1fd559e2091a4335867664aeed2a5a0","tid":220710,"uid":54373,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T07:22:22.000Z","msg":"C朗求情說,我不及我師傅傑斯的十分一<br />\n何來有罪?"},{"pid":"05e92b93ee83cd3ffca24acb2ddfca1f52df5ea3","tid":220710,"uid":372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T07:23:39.000Z","msg":"勉強左少少，反獌都撐你唔落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e98a29db9b420a62346f3750e2274253a76d62ad","tid":220710,"uid":43523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T07:24:44.000Z","msg":"見到c朗都出晒水啦<br />\n邊會係強姦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73cb974c7003026ad5b72fa53e85c74f9533e780","tid":220710,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T07:29:08.000Z","msg":"火箭連律師都撈埋"},{"